trends: There have been 2 other sightings in Rosarito

divs: Sighting DetailsI saw a bright glittery object in the sky so grabbed my camera and went outside to observe it. It hovered then started moving about and did this for about an hour. It was west over the pacific ocean, have seen it before but this time it was very bright goldish in color.
